                       throws java.lang.Exception
Adds a custom cache object to the cache pool. Cache instance must be already initialized and a name must be specified. If a similarly-named cache already exists in the pool, an Exception is raised. TM: Changed SessionedMemoryCache argument to MemoryCache.
